company.name: KMS SoftWare
company.aboutUs: Encotech is a small business, but we provide big-business services with an entrepreneurial spirit. Our human and technical resources are second-to-none. We are on the cutting-edge of the latest technologies and at the forefront of Building Information Modeling (BIM) and sustainable design. We are a boutique engineering firm that strives to be innovative, adaptable, and responsive and exceed our client’s expectations. We view engineering design as a means to transform our communities and the lives of all of us who live here. We are committed to happiness and high standards. Build lasting partnerships to create iconic engineering solutions to shape our world now and in the future.
